{"tid":728543,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京阪滋賀五日遊","createTime":"2018-07-03T22:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T12:21:38.000Z","uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d11777ef271c8c353b1f749dd89559f6130f45","tid":728543,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T22:07:15.000Z","msg":"攞咗幾日假諗住去京都郊遊踩下單車<br />\n點知旅行先嚟打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到睇天氣再睇下一步去邊<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/055219_e89cd24d7238bfa1bd682f8c8c7c220e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F055219_e89cd24d7238bfa1bd682f8c8c7c220e.jpg&h=0512e4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/055523_c0e03b4061113f1f5e6b9c5115a67a7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F055523_c0e03b4061113f1f5e6b9c5115a67a7a.jpg&h=e359b559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能係喺日本最好天嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a5e7563a81f19dfebb4a2215669a0dc544833f","tid":728543,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T22:16:50.000Z","msg":"到埗攞行李趕唔切班巴士<br />\n唯有走去搭haruka<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/061121_85ed0262cac359669d6c6c035403d8a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F061121_85ed0262cac359669d6c6c035403d8a2.jpg&h=f894fe96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/061205_6af7b3e25fa0d05ca6027768e09c9bcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F061205_6af7b3e25fa0d05ca6027768e09c9bcc.jpg&h=d4297656&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明自由席4-9卡車<br />\n啲人係都要排死4號車廂<br />\n搞到得我一條友排後幾卡 好似傻咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f4444cbcdecdb386448a25bd7a91df564b0e39","tid":728543,"uid":46464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:33:36.000Z","msg":"京板+滋賀得五日咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37aecc5438bdf154891d56a8ff31436900369ee","tid":728543,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04f4444cbcdecdb386448a25bd7a91df564b0e39","tid":728543,"uid":46464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:33:36.000Z","msg":"京板+滋賀得五日咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"滋賀係有個七夕花火大會所以特登去一去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01da948400b94b992590a8158e148bbb0d8d7451","tid":728543,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"去貴船神社中途落大雨所以番轉頭<br />\n去咗出町柳附近行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/113848_f22121723d896c43180e9e7656246607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F113848_f22121723d896c43180e9e7656246607.jpg&h=7ae913c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/114012_a0109234ce8513e83b79c409ffdbf2b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F114012_a0109234ce8513e83b79c409ffdbf2b6.jpg&h=11e95c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有飛鏢石<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/114041_f89e099d4d9e62e273d127aa3308d9a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F114041_f89e099d4d9e62e273d127aa3308d9a4.jpg&h=5e3c76fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/114656_1722a7fe51d58e5b18efdc5e968d551f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum